title: The Glenn Beck Radio Show MAR-05-2014 WED
description:
The Glenn Beck Radio Show MAR-05-2014 WED....PODCAST



The Glenn Beck Program




          Listen to The Glenn Beck Radio Program, Monday through Friday, 9am - 12pm ET



        
      
      The Glenn Beck Program - 3/5/14Wednesday, March 05, 2014 10:49 AM


Glenn kicks off the show with some good news from 2 stories
           that can be described as nothing less than miracles.  

  An update from the Romeike family, who was fighting a deportation case
      and seeking asylum in the U.S. because they wanted to homeschool their children
       and not lose them to the German government. 

 Plus, Justina Pelletier has been freed from the hospital in Boston,
                all thanks to you.  

  
  Also, Freedom works CEO Matt Kibbe, joins the program 
     to update us on the 2014 races, and how Texas voted yesterday.

  Plus, explosive hearings on the IRS scandal today.
